PresentationColumn.name: Volunteer Status
PresentationColumn.Description: Shows whether a volunteer is active.

PresentationColumn.name: Potential Volunteer Flag
PresentationColumn.Description: Denotes whether a supporter has shown interest to volunteer for us.

PresentationColumn.name: Volunteer Start Date
PresentationColumn.Description: The date of the volunteers first volunteering activity

PresentationColumn.name: Volunteer End Date
PresentationColumn.Description: The End date of the volunteers most recent volunteering activity (if the volunteer is lapsed) or null (if the volunteer is active)

PresentationColumn.name: Volunteer Estimated Hours Flag
PresentationColumn.Description: 'Y' if Owning Party has ever had hours entered against any volunteering activity, otherwise 'N'

PresentationColumn.name: Volunteer Length of Service Range
PresentationColumn.Description: The length of time somebody has volunteered between their first volunteering activity and their most recent (or if still active, today). 1 - 2 years would be anything one year or more and less than two years.
